interpretation:

The clapper board emoji can also symbolize collaboration and teamwork, indicating that the user may need to work with others to achieve their objectives. 

When this card appears in a reading, it suggests that the user is ready to embark on a new project or creative endeavor. They may feel excited and motivated to begin working towards their goals. Overall, the clapper board emoji is a positive and encouraging card that signifies the start of something new and exciting.
